Stan Lees Superhumans: Season 3
On Stan Lee's Superhumans 3 from H2, Stan Lee and the World's Most Flexible Man, Daniel Browning-Smith, travel the world testing the claims of real people who declare they have genuine superpowers.




7)  Man vs Beast 
Animals are imbued with incredible abilities, like echo-location and super-sight. This time, Stan sends Daniel on a mission to find four people who claim they have the ability to match nature's superpowered animals.
